Subject: [PATCH 091/106] =?UTF-8?q?arm64:=20dts:=20sun55i-a523:=20a=C3=B1a?=
 =?UTF-8?q?dir=20el=20controlador=20de=20reloj=20de=20CPU?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Nodo clock-controller@8817000 (allwinner,sun55i-a523-cpu-ccu) con sus
relojes de entrada (hosc/losc/iosc + pll-periph0-600m del CCU principal).
Todavía sin cablear en cpu@N (validación read-only del reloj primero).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun55i-a523.dtsi | 9 +++++++++
 1 file changed, 9 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun55i-a523.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun55i-a523.dtsi
index c1df428e2..7c490c5ee 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun55i-a523.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun55i-a523.dtsi
@@ -1163,5 +1163,14 @@ npu: npu@7122000 {
 			resets = <&mcu_ccu RST_BUS_MCU_NPU>;
 			power-domains = <&ppu PD_NPU>;
 		};
+
+		cpu_ccu: clock-controller@8817000 {
+			compatible = "allwinner,sun55i-a523-cpu-ccu";
+			reg = <0x08817000 0x4000>;
+			clocks = <&osc24M>, <&rtc CLK_OSC32K>, <&rtc CLK_IOSC>,
+				 <&ccu CLK_PLL_PERIPH0_600M>;
+			clock-names = "hosc", "losc", "iosc", "pll-periph0-600m";
+			#clock-cells = <1>;
+		};
 	};
 };
